POE/Component/Server/SimpleHTTP version 1.01
============================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	POE > 0.27
		POE::Session
		POE::Wheel::ReadWrite
		POE::Driver::SysRW
		POE::Filter::Stream
		POE::Filter::HTTPD
		POE::Component::Server::TCP

	Carp

	HTTP::Date
	HTTP::Request
	HTTP::Response

	Socket

	Sys::Hostname

